{"tid":595411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得家教法係德政","createTime":"2018-03-16T15:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T17:14:05.000Z","uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4975cbc8d26d2a4d81fef6cbd98889aba9c3511","tid":595411,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"有人大代表提出制定家庭教育法<br />\n2018/03/15 21:28<br />\n每次見到有小朋友不守規矩的新聞，第一個反應就是責怪父母沒有好好管教。這種反應很正常，這個是家庭道德倫理問題，但有人大代表就上升到立法層面，認為可以用法律手段解決這些社會問題。 <br />\n<br />\n在內地網上，經常都可以看到這些片段，有時候父母不單沒有阻止，甚至還主動幫兒子點煙，在旁拍片一起笑，不過短片看得多，實際情況又有多普遍呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線中國組在街頭隨便問，十人有九人都稱見過類似的事，近年這類問題都在海外引起不少關注，有人大代表建議要解決問題，要由小孩的家教開始做起。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧麗是全國婦聯副主席，她今年聯署提出的一個議案，就是要制定家庭教育法，簡單來說，即是用法律規範家長如何教育孩子。她指家教是國民教育的重要部份，要將社會主義核心價值觀融入家庭，要由法律政策層面，培育具有中國特色的家庭教育思想，而如果子女將來做錯事，做父母的都有責任，但何謂家庭教育失當呢？鄧麗指現在全國有上百萬留守兒童，很多父母為了打工糊口，以致無暇教育子女，這類人都需要特別指引，不過連教育後代這些家事，都寫入法例又是否合理？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她強調法例主要都是指引一批家長如何教育子女，罰則只會在特殊情況下使用，鄧麗指家庭教育法目前已在重慶和貴州省開始試行，當地家長都非常歡迎，所以覺得是時候放上全國平台討論。"},{"pid":"d44cd4923bc70721df22c57bfb3b0c481acaf2b4","tid":595411,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"唔識教仔好心咪撚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c4690494ade1a7aab94de01fa6fecc3802beeb","tid":595411,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd261cbb79d4f08b5e933a102fc0d7ca5caf95ec","tid":595411,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人需要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95943f0f94dce84c927743e7cd82155c66db3413","tid":595411,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"我估都係重推 誅九族 前攞嚟試水溫既政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad44fb674dd31fc8c47cf90d6fbdcfb670a03b8","tid":595411,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd261cbb79d4f08b5e933a102fc0d7ca5caf95ec","tid":595411,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人需要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826f7f79811f976f82432d730d5d3c1775211d96","tid":595411,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522748f73e6a0d0c31bf39fa25f1614e5eb8d7f0","tid":595411,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9be5873532a845c9104d94012daeca3f3175d6e","tid":595411,"uid":40463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"522748f73e6a0d0c31bf39fa25f1614e5eb8d7f0","tid":595411,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"搞到啲高官有錢人爭住將啲親戚送去外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}